\">{{cite web| url = http://www.altfg.com/blog/awards/florida-film-critics-awards-2008/| title = Florida Film Critics Awards 2008| last = Arthur| first = Deborah| date = 2008-12-18| publisher = Alternative Film Guide| accessdate = 2009-04-27| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090224000824/http://www.altfg.com/blog/awards/florida-film-critics-awards-2008/| archive-date = 24 February 2009| url-status = dead| df = dmy-all}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"2\"|[[G\u00f6teborg Film Festival]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2008\n| Nordic Film Prize\n!\n| {{won}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"2\"|<ref name=\"GoteborgAward\"/>\n|-\n| Nordic Vision Award\n| Hoyte Van Hoytema\n| {{won}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|[[Goya Awards]]\n| [[24th Goya Awards|24 February 2010]]\n|[[Goya Award for Best European Film|Best European Film]]\n!\n| {{nom}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref name=\"goya\">{{cite web|url=http://noticias.terra.es/2010/genteycultura/0215/actualidad/slumdog-millionaire-goya-a-la-mejor-pelicula-europea.aspx |title=\"Slumdog Millionaire\", Goya a la mejor pel\u00edcula europea |date=15 February 2010 |publisher=[[Terra Networks]] |language=Spanish |accessdate=19 February 2010 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120226204811/http://noticias.terra.es/2010/genteycultura/0215/actualidad/slumdog-millionaire-goya-a-la-mejor-pelicula-europea.aspx |archivedate=26 February 2012 |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" rowspan=\"7\"|[[Guldbagge Awards]]\n| rowspan=\"7\" | [[44th Guldbagge Awards|12 January 2009]]\n| Best Achievement (B\u00e4sta prestation)\n| Eva Nor\u00e9n\n| {{won}}\n|style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"7\"|<ref name=\"sfi\"/>\n|-\n| Best Achievement (B\u00e4sta prestation)\n| Per Sundstr\u00f6m, Jonas Jansson, Patrik Str\u00f6mdahl\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Guldbagge Award for Best Cinematography|Best Cinematography]] (B\u00e4sta foto)\n| Hoyte Van Hoytema\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[Guldbagge Award for Best Director|Best Direction]]